    <item>
      <title>如果特朗普先发制人，巴西总统卢拉将实施报复性关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/brazil-s-lula-floats-retaliatory-tariffs-if-trump-strikes-first</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普对巴西产品征收新的关税，巴西准备做出回应，但他希望改善与美国的贸易关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/brazil-s-lula-floats-retaliatory-tariffs-if-trump-strikes-first</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 16:08:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果叛军如何取得进展并威胁与卢旺达开战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/dr-congo-how-m23-rebel-advances-threaten-war-with-rwanda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国东部多年来一直饱受战乱之苦，数百万人丧命，大批民众流离失所。2025 年初，与卢旺达结盟的叛军占领了刚果的主要贸易枢纽戈马，威胁着引发这两个中非国家之间的全面冲突，标志着局势的升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/dr-congo-how-m23-rebel-advances-threaten-war-with-rwanda</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 16:08:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普第二次攻击全球气候秩序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-30/the-global-climate-order-teeters-under-second-assault-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普第二次退出《巴黎协定》，对气候行动来说，这是一个更加动荡的时期，民粹主义的兴起和企业的撤退给美国撤退增加了更大的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-30/the-global-climate-order-teeters-under-second-assault-by-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 14:39:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
